%% Diagram: Sync vs async vs semi-sync replication timing
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant L as Leader
    participant F1 as Follower 1
    participant F2 as Follower 2

    Note over C,F2: Async — leader acks before followers replicate
    C->>L: write(x)
    L-->>C: ack
    L->>F1: replicate(x)
    L->>F2: replicate(x)

    Note over C,F2: Semi-sync — wait for at least one follower
    C->>L: write(x)
    L->>F1: replicate(x)
    L->>F2: replicate(x)
    F1-->>L: ack
    L-->>C: ack
    F2-->>L: ack (background)

    Note over C,F2: Sync — wait for quorum or all followers
    C->>L: write(x)
    L->>F1: replicate(x)
    L->>F2: replicate(x)
    F1-->>L: ack
    F2-->>L: ack
    L-->>C: ack
